chunks.html_content: Contact the police if you’re being stalked - you have a right to feel safe in your home and workplace.

Contact the police if you’re being stalked - you have a right to feel safe in your home and workplace.

chunks.html_content: Stalking is illegal and can include being followed or constantly harassed by another person - for example being sent unwanted emails.
